    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks, that makes sense. can you get more specific though? like, when you say \"neat and controlled\" hair, what are you actually thinking of? i have some clients who have natural textures or styles that aren't necessarily \"smooth\" or \"sleek\"—is it better for them to try and tame that look for these meetings, or is there a way to make it look professional?",
